OL,3,CBondi Beach terror attack hero charged
OL,4,Cwith assaulting his father
OL,6,FA man hailed a hero for stopping one
OL,7,Fof the Bondi Beach terror attackers
OL,8,Fhas been charged with assaulting his
OL,9,Ffather.
OL,11,FAhmed Al Ahmed, 44, is accused of
OL,12,Fattacking his elderly father and
OL,13,Fputting him in a headlock in his own
OL,14,Fhome in Bankstown, Sydney, in March
OL,15,Fearlier this year, ITV News'
OL,16,FAustralian partner 7News reports.
OL,18,FHe was charged with domestic violence,
OL,19,Fcommon assault and stalking, and must
OL,20,Fattend court on July 29.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
