OL,3,CBondi Beach terror attack hero charged
OL,4,Cwith assaulting his father
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPolice have also taken out an
OL,12,FApprehended Violence Order (AVO)
OL,13,Fagainst Ahmed, which prevents him from
OL,14,Fcontacting or coming within 100 metres
OL,15,Fof his father, 7News reports.
OL,17,FNew South Wales police confirmed an
OL,18,Falleged assault from March 9 had been
OL,19,Freported to officers on March 15.
