OL,3,CBondi Beach terror attack hero charged
OL,4,Cwith assaulting his father
OL,6,FAhmed made international headlines in
OL,7,FDecember when he ran towards one of
OL,8,Ftwo gunmen who had opened fire on a
OL,9,FHanukkah celebration on Bondi Beach,
OL,10,Fin Sydney, before wrestling his weapon
OL,11,Ffrom him.
OL,13,FThe terror attack left 15 people dead
OL,14,Fand dozens more injured, including two
OL,15,Fpolice officers.
OL,17,FAhmed was shot multiple times in the
OL,18,Fleft arm and underwent surgery for his
OL,19,Finjuries, with Australian Prime
OL,20,FMinister Anthony Albanese visiting him
OL,21,Fin hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
