OL,3,CBondi Beach terror attack hero charged
OL,4,Cwith assaulting his father
OL,6,FTens of thousands of people donated to
OL,7,Fa fundraiser set up for him, which
OL,8,Fsurpassed 2.3 million Australian
OL,9,Fdollars (#1,142,525) less than five
OL,10,Fdays after the attack.
OL,12,FAt the time, his father said he felt
OL,13,F"pride and honour" because Ahmed was
OL,14,F"a hero of Australia".
OL,16,FIt comes as two of Ahmed's brothers
OL,17,Fface criminal charges, after allegedly
OL,18,Fthreatening him over the phone and
OL,19,Fdemanding he pay them each 100,000
OL,20,FAustralian dollars (#74,300).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
